net.usikkert.kouinject.beandata
Class BeanData

java.lang.Object
  net.usikkert.kouinject.beandata.BeanData

public class BeanData
extends java.lang.Object

This class describes the bean meta-data needed to instantiate a new bean to a consistent state.

Author:
Christian Ihle

Constructor Detail

BeanData

public BeanData(java.lang.Class<?> beanClass,
                ConstructorData constructor,
                java.util.List<InjectionPoint> injectionPoints,
                boolean isSingleton)
Constructs a new BeanData instance for describing the defined class.

Parameters:
beanClass - The class this BeanData will describe.
constructor - Optional meta-data for the constructor to invoke on beanClass. If this is null then the bean can not be instantiated.
injectionPoints - Meta-data for the injection points in beanClass that requires dependency injection.
isSingleton - If this bean is a singleton.
